OL,3,CCouncil bin boss filmed removing pro-
OL,4,Cstrike placards from Birmingham streets
OL,6,FThe councillor in charge of
OL,7,FBirmingham's bin service has been
OL,8,Ffilmed removing pro-strike placards
OL,9,Ffrom streets in the city during the
OL,10,Fongoing refuse workers' dispute.
OL,12,FIn footage shared exclusively with ITV
OL,13,FNews Central, Majid Mahmood can be
OL,14,Fseen taking down posters supporting
OL,15,Fstriking bin workers.
OL,17,FThe signs read: "We support the
OL,18,FBirmingham bin workers: No cuts to
OL,19,Fpay."
OL,26,@yD@QOU{D@EO]
