OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772193825
OL,3,CCouncil bin boss filmed removing pro-
OL,4,Cstrike placards from Birmingham streets
OL,6,FCllr Mahmood is the cabinet member
OL,7,Fresponsible for waste services at
OL,8,FBirmingham City Council.
OL,10,FThe authority is locked in a long-
OL,11,Frunning dispute with refuse workers
OL,12,Fover pay and conditions.
OL,14,FCllr Mahmood told ITV News he removed
OL,15,Fthe posters following complaints from
OL,16,Fresidents and said it was part of
OL,17,Froutine action he takes in the area.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
