PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772193825
OL,3,CCouncil bin boss filmed removing pro-
OL,4,Cstrike placards from Birmingham streets
OL,6,F"I regularly remove unauthorised
OL,7,Fattachments in the area as it is
OL,8,Fsomething residents complain about, so
OL,9,Fthis is not unusual," he said.
OL,11,F"On that day I also removed posters
OL,12,Fadvertising blind companies, takeaways
OL,13,Fand tuition companies.
OL,15,F"Flyposting isn't permitted and many
OL,16,Fof these posters were becoming
OL,17,Fhazardous to drivers and pedestrians.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]sD@AOUwD@AOU
