PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772193825
OL,3,CCouncil bin boss filmed removing pro-
OL,4,Cstrike placards from Birmingham streets
OL,6,F"Additionally, unlawful advertising is
OL,7,Funfair on businesses paying to
OL,8,Fadvertise their companies using the
OL,9,Fproper channels.
OL,11,F"So let's all keep our community
OL,12,Fclean, safe and fair for everyone.
OL,13,FPosters that have been removed can be
OL,14,Fcollected from me by 27 February,
OL,15,Fotherwise they will be taken for
OL,16,Frecycling."
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@KO]
