PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772193825
OL,3,CCouncil bin boss filmed removing pro-
OL,4,Cstrike placards from Birmingham streets
OL,6,FA Unite spokesperson said: "These
OL,7,Fsigns were put up with the support of
OL,8,Flocal businesses, the local community
OL,9,Fand local residents and we question
OL,10,Fwhether it is appropriate for a
OL,11,Fcouncillor to stifle criticism of his
OL,12,Fdecisions by cutting down signs.
OL,14,F"It has been seven months since
OL,15,FBirmingham City Council walked away
OL,16,Ffrom bin strike negotiations, Majid
OL,17,FMahmood would be better spending his
OL,18,Ftime working on a return to
OL,19,Fnegotiations."
OL,26,@nD@\OU{D@NO]
