OL,3,CCouncil bin boss filmed removing pro-
OL,4,Cstrike placards from Birmingham streets
OL,6,FThe strike has caused significant
OL,7,Fdisruption across Birmingham, with
OL,8,Fbins going uncollected in some areas
OL,9,Fand tensions running high between the
OL,10,Fcouncil and workers.
OL,12,FAn all-out election on Birmingham City
OL,13,FCouncil is scheduled for 7 May.
